{"tid":1702041,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"事隔24小時 黑警未對輪姦少女單野回應 事實擺在眼前","createTime":"2019-11-09T13:25:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-09T13:53:03.000Z","uid":247180,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"1d7da654af273631457f0fd918c1d1ed36f98f35","tid":1702041,"uid":247180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:25:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db5a6ad11378fa8fedde89e7b37b0d8402917430","tid":1702041,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:32:02.000Z","msg":"冇做過 點認"},{"pid":"4abc7f6a7cbe0ac36cb70ad4506022d2632f47c1","tid":1702041,"uid":35930,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db5a6ad11378fa8fedde89e7b37b0d8402917430","tid":1702041,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:32:02.000Z","msg":"冇做過 點認"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:34:15.000Z","msg":"警方：接報有人在荃灣警署被強姦　指控與調查結果不吻合<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1702059\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1702059</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"13e3b73bea5f9ee75a674d3a4f1cca65cd91b0ca","tid":1702041,"uid":35090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:34:28.000Z","msg":"班仆街諗緊點兜啊屌你老母"},{"pid":"d33007466af17c65c1fe927946bec53cfaa1b876","tid":1702041,"uid":34295,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:34:59.000Z","msg":"【警稱接報有人在荃灣警署被強姦】<br />\n【指控與調查結果不吻合】<br />\n<br />\n網上有傳一名女子被捕後遭警方性侵，其後要到伊利沙伯醫院接受墮胎手術。警方回應查詢時表示，投訴警察課上月22日收到一名律師代表報案，指他的當事人聲稱於9月27日，於荃灣警署內被強姦。<br />\n<br />\n警方說，由於指控嚴重，隨即由新界南總區重案組調查，截至目前，報案人的指控內容，與調查結果並不吻合，警方會就相關指控繼續調查。<br />\n<br />\n醫管局回應說，不評論網上個別個案的傳言，重申保障病人私隱的重要性，並呼籲公眾不要到醫院範圍集會，以及作非醫療有關的活動，以免影響服務運作。"},{"pid":"b053437088768394a88c20bae38972d1ebe8af9a","tid":1702041,"uid":73586,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:36:05.000Z","msg":"調查左啲乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e64606ce3dde0620ab89e83536c7a6e889872ffe","tid":1702041,"uid":119157,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:36:52.000Z","msg":"要驗DNA啦喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4d5b5b6b56b972f00bc7a7713256de0e77de899","tid":1702041,"uid":147317,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"db5a6ad11378fa8fedde89e7b37b0d8402917430","tid":1702041,"uid":35930,"like":0,"dislike":19,"score":-19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:32:02.000Z","msg":"冇做過 點認"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:37:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n狗"},{"pid":"93dfe5fcd2231bb1c3dc434b4a1c31d6d74b1325","tid":1702041,"uid":126609,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7287e95a1c22247c519de73777f303cb32b7af44","tid":1702041,"uid":292076,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"93dfe5fcd2231bb1c3dc434b4a1c31d6d74b1325","tid":1702041,"uid":126609,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:39:08.000Z","msg":"墮"},{"pid":"29fb73808e6b1d86a23ddbd0ea9ca5a5a11ece32","tid":1702041,"uid":74827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"93dfe5fcd2231bb1c3dc434b4a1c31d6d74b1325","tid":1702041,"uid":126609,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:38:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T13:39:15.000Z","msg":"Bye 五毛"},{"pid":"0624eec2575ccfdbc5a62a1f65e0e2eba6e7aadc","tid":1702041,"uid":74155,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score"